Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,祈禱?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是追悼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,追悼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他正頂著太陽往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經不行了  出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是規則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你和姐姐我之前見過面來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是錯覺嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,注意太陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽來了  萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一直等著媽媽  真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚想吃什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚吃的是咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就吃漢堡肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,茶泡飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我家萌香真是老成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  萌香?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽  你出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  原來是不能走出影子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  這就是規則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那媽媽還真得注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要送給爺爺的禮物  好好地帶在身上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  帶著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,圓石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我還畫了幅爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体 第二版\fs40\bord0\shad0\c&H090517&\frz5.048\pos(622,133.144)}我愛    爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  畫得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺肯定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來  萌香你真會畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,長大了當畫家?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,美姬社
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香長大了要美姬社!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,美姬社?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是美術社?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來  爺爺說他前些日子還是美術社的顧問老師來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺也美術社?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他給你講講吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,出局了
